23
00:01:41,031 --> 00:01:43,389
And your hair looks different.

24
00:01:45,611 --> 00:01:48,727
- You look great, Gina.
- That's good of you to say that.

25
00:01:49,949 --> 00:01:52,439
Makes you look,
I don't know, softer somehow.

26
